// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1709 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 24de1387-8e46-5d2b-9628-6ec8d5a6328c

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2*" or process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2023*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
